descriptionHtml:
Sorry,I'm not good at English.
This Mod Add 15 poses. 
But, it is poor so, because it was something that I made for myself.

It requires FNIS to use the Pose.
Usage Please have a look at the FNIS.

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/11811]Fores New Idles in Skyrim - FNIS[/url]

My mod is overrides the hkx file in the FNIS. 
Please rename or back up hkx file.
You can use any " FNIS EIS - Miscellaneous " or " Pinup_Poser " if you rename the hkx file. 
NotICE : There are differences in some pose by pose mod or Body mod.
